'''氯代烷'''（[[File:Chloro-group.svg|40px]]），是指[[烷烃|烷烴]][[分子|分子]]中的一個或多個氫原子被氯[[取代|取代]]的[[有机化合物|有機化合物]]，屬[[卤代烃|鹵代烴]]的一種。

== 製備 ==
氯代烴可由[[烷烃|烷烴]]和[[氯气|氯氣]]反應得到，屬於[[自由基取代反應|自由基鹵代反應]]的一種。反應分「鏈引發」、「鏈增長」、「鏈終止」三步驟<ref>{{cite web |author1=Dr. Ian Hunt, |title=Chapter 4: Alcohols and Alkyl Halides |url=https://www.chem.ucalgary.ca/courses/351/Carey5th/Ch04/ch4-4-2.html |accessdate=2021-07-28 |language=en |quote=Note that it contains three distinct type of steps |archive-date=2021-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210728154015/https://www.chem.ucalgary.ca/courses/351/Carey5th/Ch04/ch4-4-2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。產物通常是多個[[氯代烷|氯代烷]]的[[混合物|混合物]]。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Industrial & Engineering Chemistry|volume=28|issue=3|language=en|issn=0019-7866|date=1936-03|pages=333–339|doi=10.1021/ie50315a017|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ie50315a017|title=Chlorination of Paraffins 1|accessdate=2020-07-12|author=H. B. Hass, E. T. McBee, Paul Weber|archive-date=2021-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210804143345/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ie50315a017|dead-url=no}}</ref>


[[烯烃|烯]]類、[[炔烃|炔類]]跟[[盐酸|鹽酸]]反應，經過[[鹵氫化作用|鹵氫化作用]]可生成氯代烷。反應機理為[[亲电加成反应|親電加成反應]]，第一步為[[π電子|π電子]]進攻氫氯酸，生成[[碳正离子|碳陽離子]]和氯離子，然後氯離子進攻碳陽離子生成氯代烷<ref>March, Jerry; (1985). Advanced Organic Chemistry reactions, mechanisms and structure (3rd ed.). New York: John Wiley & Sons, inc. {{ISBN|0-471-85472-7}}</ref>。反應遵從[[馬氏規則|馬氏規則]]<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Catalysis|volume=252|issue=1|language=en|date=2007-11-15|pages=23–29|doi=10.1016/j.jcat.2007.09.002|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0021951707003442|title=Selective formation of chloroethane by the hydrochlorination of ethene using zinc catalysts|accessdate=2020-07-12|author=M Conte, T Davies, A Carley, A Herzing, C Kiely, G Hutchings|archive-date=2018-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702000554/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0021951707003442|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而由於碳陽離子是個平面，氯離子可以從平面上方或下方進攻，有機會生成帶手性的氯代烷。機理如下：
