== 反應 ==
===[[双分子亲核取代反应|親核取代反應]]===
氯的電負性大，是個[[电负性|電負性]]強且穩定的[[离去基团|離去基團]]。在[[单分子亲核取代反应|單分子親核取代反應]]裡面，氯以氯離子的形式離開，生成碳陽離子，其後氯離子進攻碳陽離子生成新化合物。三級氯代烷通常以單分子機理進行反應<ref>{{cite web |title=SN1 and SN2 Reactions |url=https://web.iit.edu/sites/web/files/departments/academic-affairs/academic-resource-center/pdfs/SN1_SN2.pdf |accessdate=2021-07-28 |language=en |format=pdf |archive-date=2019-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512112006/https://web.iit.edu/sites/web/files/departments/academic-affairs/academic-resource-center/pdfs/SN1_SN2.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[双分子亲核取代反应|雙分子親核取代反應]]中，[[亲核体|親核試劑]]攻擊連着氯的碳原子，然後形成一個[[配位数|五配位]]的[[过渡态|過渡態]]。氯很快離去，形成新化合物。一級氯代烷通常按雙分子的機理進行親核取代<ref>{{cite web |title=8.4 Comparison and Competition Between SN1, SN2, E1 and E2 |url=https://kpu.pressbooks.pub/organicchemistry/chapter/8-4-comparison-and-competition-between-sn1-sn2-e1-and-e2/ |publisher=Pressbooks |accessdate=2021-07-28 |language=en |archive-date=2021-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210728181552/https://kpu.pressbooks.pub/organicchemistry/chapter/8-4-comparison-and-competition-between-sn1-sn2-e1-and-e2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

例如[[氯乙烷|氯乙烷]]與[[氢氧根|氫氧根]]離子發生S<sub>N</sub>2生成[[乙醇|乙醇]]和[[氯化物|氯離子]]：
:EtCl + NaOH → EtOH + NaCl

